Service Cloud Functionality with My Service Journey (Beta)

Discover the many ways Service Cloud can help you deliver instant, personalized service and support to your customers with My Service Journey.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions

My Service Journey details the full feature set of Service Cloud, helping you quickly determine how Salesforce can further your business goals. It lists cloud functionalities in short form, called capabilities.

You can filter capabilities by:

* Business area
* Available edition
* Newest ones

Identify Quick Wins — capabilities with no or low implementation barriers — to get started right away.

Save and share relevant capabilities with other team members. If you find a capability that's relevant but don't have access, reach out to Salesforce account executives directly in My Service Journey.

Add My Service Journey to your console app's navigation menu for enhanced exploration of Service Cloud capabilities.

Edit Profile Access to My Service Journey
Limit access to My Service Journey in Setup.
title: Service Cloud Features and Functionality
